ActEmployment Insurance Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Employment Insurance Regulations
PrecisRegulations amending the EMPLOYMENT INSURANCE REGULATIONS in order to facilitate willing compliance when a person is placed in quarantine by a public health official to remain in quarantine and remove the risk of persons attempting to return to work.
